function getNetworkType() {
  var ua = navigator.userAgent
  var networkStr = ua.match(/NetType\/\w+/) ? ua.match(/NetType\/\w+/)[0] : 'NetType/other'
  networkStr = networkStr.toLowerCase().replace('nettype/', '')
  var networkType
  switch (networkStr) {
    case 'wifi':
      networkType = 'wifi'
      break
    case '5g':
      networkType = 'mobile'
      break
    case '4g':
      networkType = 'mobile'
      break
    case '3g':
      networkType = 'mobile'
      break
    case '3gnet':
      networkType = 'mobile'
      break
    case '2g':
      networkType = 'mobile'
      break
    default:
      networkType = 'other'
  }
